&lt;p&gt;As an Account Executive, you will be an early sales hire and have a critical role in growing an early-stage startup.&amp;nbsp; You will work alongside the CEO and be responsible for expanding our customer base, driving revenue growth, and establishing trusted relationships with our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
