&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect and identify new sales opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct in-depth research to understand prospects&#39; needs, pain points, and existing software solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a robust sales pipeline, utilizing various channels such as cold calling, email outreach, industry conferences, and referrals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead product demonstrations and presentations to educate prospects on the benefits and features of our software solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and deliver compelling sales proposals, tailored to each prospect&#39;s specific requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate pricing, terms, and contracts in alignment with company guidelines and customer expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the implementation and customer success teams to ensure a smooth transition from sale to onboarding and ongoing support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on sales activities, pipeline progress, and revenue forecasts using our CRM system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up to date with industry trends, market conditions, and competitor activities to identify potential opportunities and threats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with CEO to refine sales strategies, pricing models, and go-to-market plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
