&lt;li&gt;Concise, persuasive, and authentic communicator both verbally and in written communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent listener and demonstrated ability to problem solve with key stakeholders at all levels, from executives to end-users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embraces ownership mindset with ability to take initiative in a fast-paced start-up setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills with excellent attention to detail&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superb judgment and integrity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with CRM software and sales tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Personal connection to autism or autism care is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
