&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end sales function and help define what &quot;great sales&quot; looks like at Passage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the CEO and marketing to shape our overall go-to-market strategy, priorities, and roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the foundation for a scalable sales org — process, tools, CRM hygiene, forecasting, and ways of working.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define the future structure of the sales team and hire, onboard, and develop reps over time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay close to the most important deals, providing coaching and support that improves win rates and helps the team close business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Strategy, Positioning &amp;amp; Competitive Selling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own how we sell — sharpening our pitch and value proposition so it
